(26177, 24781, 2627, 11, 'Black Book', 'Storyteller身後沉重的黑書，究竟是怎麼來的呢?\r\n"這是一個古老的故事，關於這位說故事者與他拖著的黑書。"', '2010-06-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 9, '[Narrator]\r\nThe hero spent his night in the tavern\r\nA place so-called "Happy Ending"\r\nThere''s an interesting guy with a funny name Storyteller who had told lots of stories \r\nIt took a whole night long\r\nAnd finally the guy asked a question, it''s a silly one, "would you be my story?"\r\n"would you be my story?"\r\nAfter a casual "yes"\r\nThe hero disappeared!!\r\n\r\nAs if he had never existed. NO!\r\nNever exist! no!\r\n\r\n[Black Book & Storyteller]\r\n"One way or another\r\nyou will be ours"\r\nIt''s an ancient story\r\nabout the teller and the black book he drags\r\n\r\n[Narrator]\r\nMy wrong let''s add another raw\r\nFade another sin\r\n\r\nI can still hear them shout\r\nLoud and clear I hear them shout\r\n\r\n[Black Book & Storyteller]\r\nTake it we never have enough we take it\r\nWe never ever have enough we take it\r\nAll! All~~\r\n\r\nWe take it we never ever have enough we take it we take it\r\nwe take it we never ever satisfied we take now we take it\r\n\r\nwe never ever satisfied now we get it\r\n\r\n\r\n[Narrator]\r\nsomething wrong with it\r\nThe song''s complete wrong\r\nWhat''s going on here?\r\nI must hit the wrong button\r\nNow stop it please\r\nStop it! Stop it!! Stop it!!!\r\nstop!\r\n\r\n[Storyteller]\r\nIn the silence\r\nthere''s a faint sound\r\nthe quill''s dancing on a vellum\r\nHis thin hand held it firmly\r\nWrote down every subtle details\r\nInk''s flowing \r\nWords were forming\r\nreflected those what he had seen\r\nEnthusiasm\r\nNever stopping\r\nHe''s a faithful historian\r\n\r\n[The Historian]\r\n"I wanna see it all\r\nEverything is happening so soon\r\nI''ve been detained\r\nby the dreary hand-writing job"\r\n\r\n\r\n[Storyteller]\r\nHow long have I been looking for \r\nA companion, a suitable soul\r\nThe one with a strong ambition, aspiration\r\nto watch the whole world\r\nDiscerning, fidelity\r\nFeel no shame to take it all\r\nRight here, right in front of me\r\nI finally meet the right one\r\n\r\n[Storyteller][The Historian]\r\nWould you come with me? (Yes I come with you)\r\nEternal life I grand you (Eternal life I long for)\r\nin a better form (In a better form)\r\nbehold!! (Behold)\r\n\r\n[Black Book]\r\nReady or not?! \r\nHere we come!\r\nI''m in a new form of a pretty black book\r\nJourney on to replenish (reload) the stock\r\nFeed me with all the colorful souls \r\nEven the mightiest warriors, sliest dragons, wisest kings, the most powerful gods\r\nhad fallen into our tricks\r\n"Would you like to hear my stories?"\r\nAll creatures shall bow down to us\r\nWe are so invincible\r\nTake it all take it all my master\r\n\r\n[Black Book]\r\nWherever you go \r\nI will follow forever\r\nNo matter what happens\r\nTogether shall we be always\r\n\r\n\r\n[Black Book]\r\nA million year has passed by\r\nPassion subsided\r\nEveryday is as calm as it should be\r\nIt''s a sin to trap them\r\nI''m growing tired of enduring the scream, the shriek, and the shrill\r\nsounds from within\r\n\r\n[Black Book]\r\nWords are falling out\r\nIt''s too much for me to take\r\nPages are burning inside of me\r\nI can''t hold it any longer\r\n\r\n[Black Book]\r\nMaybe just one\r\nI try to reverse the magic\r\nSet one free\r\nto alleviate the ache\r\nWell I success\r\nwho''s the next one?\r\nLet''s do it again unbeknown to the master \r\n[Storyteller]\r\nWell I feel something is happening\r\nWhat''s wrong with this chill atmosphere?\r\nWhat have you done?!\r\nDon''t you know these people were willing to be part of my words?\r\nWell I entrusted you with all my stories\r\nYou dumped them all like worthless rubbish\r\nThe promise has broken\r\nI shall leave you rot here\r\nThis has to be ended right here right now\r\n\r\nSolo\r\n\r\n[Black Book]\r\nFree at last, no more pain\r\nA blank book without content\r\nSo fragile, uncertain\r\nIn the middle of nowhere\r\nThis is my redemption\r\nfor all the captive years\r\nEternal loneliness\r\nA black book full of white pages\r\nFree at last\r\nNo more pain\r\nSo fragile\r\nUncertain\r\nEternal, forever \r\nA deep dark black book I am\r\nWithin me you will find (I''m still) the same old historian\r\n\r\n[Storyteller]\r\nHere I stand alone in sorrow\r\nBetrayed by my best friend\r\nHe did not understand\r\nThe essence of my stories\r\nWell I am just a wordless storyteller\r\nWould you hear my story?\r\nWould you be my story?', '', 565, '', 'vicnest', 'vicnest', 'vicnest', 'Vicnest Music Studio', '', 1, 1, 0, '2010-06-30 14:18:00', '2015-03-12 13:42:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
