(26224, 73702, 2639, 1, 'The Castle of Angels-When the story begins (intro)', 'Legend has it that long time ago above the cloud,\r\nthere was a secret castle lived with angels of all\r\nkinds. So people called it The Castle of Angels.\r\nHeavily guarded as it was, all angels there had\r\nto follow the demand of the elder, Gabriel.\r\nThey had to work all day and couldn''t be in touch \r\nwith the human being on the ground or they would be \r\npunished to deprive of the power as an angel...\r\nDays after days, years after years, the sky was always so\r\nquiet until one day in the midnight, a young angel broke the \r\nrules, he secretly flied down to the ground, and decided to\r\nsacrifice for his love...', '2010-04-16 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 19, '', '', 96, '', 'Larrisim', '', 'Larrisim', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-07-02 22:44:28', '2015-03-12 13:42:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(26225, 73702, 2639, 3, '青樓', '婀娜的體態 如玉般的肌膚 \r\n輕盈的步伐點滴翩翩起舞 \r\n細嫩的雙手擺動柔美旋律 \r\n嘻笑辱罵 載歌載舞 \r\n日復一日 年復一年 \r\n能再維持幾回寒暑? 色衰 \r\n粉底之下隱藏著是哀愁 \r\n胭脂後的是憂傷 是鬱卒 \r\n微笑的面具 無奈被掩飾的多好 \r\n還是得擠在男人之間 滿足\r\n野獸似的垂涎 貪婪的財主 \r\n不得不再彈一曲 再跳一段舞', '2010-04-16 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 17, '', '', 239, '', 'Larrisim', 'Larrisim', 'Larrisim', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-07-02 22:46:34', '2015-03-12 13:42:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
